msgid ""
"Build Klein for Ray DataStream programs with precise record, UDF, "
"batching, async, partitioning, and failure semantics."
msgstr "使用精确的记录、UDF、批处理、异步、分区和故障语义构建 Klein for Ray DataStream 程序。"

msgid "DataStream programming guide"
msgstr "DataStream 编程指南"

msgid ""
"Klein programs build a lazy graph of sources, transformations, and "
"terminal sinks. The whole graph runs either on the Ray Data batch backend"
" or on Klein's native streaming backend. The selected backend matters: "
"both accept the same core transformation calls, but batching, scheduling,"
" schema discovery, and failure recovery belong to the backend that "
"executes the graph."
msgstr ""
"Klein 程序会构建一个由源、转换和终端接收器组成的惰性图。整个图要么在 Ray Data 批处理后端上运行，要么在 Klein "
"原生流处理后端上运行。选择哪个后端非常重要：二者接受相同的核心转换调用，但批处理、调度、模式发现和故障恢复由实际执行图的后端负责。"

msgid ""
"Use the [operator compatibility matrix](operator-compatibility.md) before"
" mixing batch-only and streaming-only operations, and inspect the "
"complete graph with `ray.klein.explain(...)` before submitting it."
msgstr ""
"在混用仅批处理和仅流处理的操作之前，请查看[算子兼容性矩阵](operator-compatibility.md)，并在提交前使用 "
"`ray.klein.explain(...)` 检查完整图。"

msgid "Records and schemas"
msgstr "记录与模式"

msgid ""
"The portable DataStream record is a mapping from column name to Python "
"value:"
msgstr "可移植的 DataStream 记录是从列名到 Python 值的映射："

msgid ""
"Native streaming sources and operators require every emitted data record "
"to be a `Mapping`. Wrap a scalar or object in a named field instead of "
"emitting it directly:"
msgstr "原生流处理源和算子要求每条发出的数据记录都是 `Mapping`。请将标量或对象包装在具名字段中，而不要直接发出："

msgid ""
"`ChangelogRow` is also a mapping, with row-kind metadata used by "
"continuous SQL and changelog-aware connectors. Ordinary dictionaries are "
"append-only rows."
msgstr "`ChangelogRow` 也是映射，其中带有供连续 SQL 和支持变更日志的连接器使用的行种类元数据。普通字典表示仅追加行。"

msgid ""
"Klein does not require a declared static schema for an ordinary native "
"stream. Mapping keys are the column names, and value types are checked by"
" the UDF or connector that consumes them. Consequently, a graph can be "
"constructed even when two branches produce incompatible fields; the error"
" appears only when an operator or sink tries to use those fields. "
"Validate important contracts in application code and keep branch schemas "
"consistent before `union()`."
msgstr ""
"Klein 不要求普通原生流声明静态模式。映射键就是列名，值类型由消费它们的 UDF "
"或连接器检查。因此，即使两个分支生成不兼容的字段，也仍能构建图；只有当算子或接收器尝试使用这些字段时才会出现错误。请在应用代码中验证重要契约，并在"
" `union()` 之前保持各分支模式一致。"

msgid ""
"`DataStream.schema()` is a terminal operation. In batch mode it reports "
"the schema discovered by the underlying Ray Data `Dataset`; it is not a "
"schema declaration for a native streaming graph. Connector formats can "
"impose their own schemas and changelog modes. See the [connector "
"catalog](connectors/index.md) and [SQL guide](sql.md) for those "
"contracts."
msgstr ""
"`DataStream.schema()` 是终端操作。在批处理模式下，它报告底层 Ray Data `Dataset` "
"发现的模式；它不是原生流处理图的模式声明。连接器格式可以施加自己的模式和变更日志模式。有关这些契约，请参阅[连接器目录](connectors/index.md)和"
" [SQL 指南](sql.md)。"

msgid "Row-shaped and columnar records"
msgstr "行式记录与列式记录"

msgid ""
"Without operator batching, a UDF receives one row mapping at a time. With"
" native streaming batching enabled, Klein converts an arrival-ordered "
"group of rows into a column mapping:"
msgstr "未启用算子批处理时，UDF 每次接收一个行映射。启用原生流批处理后，Klein 会将一组按到达顺序排列的行转换为列映射："

msgid ""
"A columnar result must itself be a mapping, every column must be "
"sequence-like, and all columns must have the same length. A malformed "
"result fails the UDF invocation. Zero-length output represents no rows."
msgstr "列式结果本身必须是映射，每一列都必须类似序列，而且所有列长度必须相同。格式错误的结果会导致 UDF 调用失败。长度为零的输出表示没有行。"

msgid ""
"For code that must run on either backend, prefer row mappings for `map`, "
"`flat_map`, and `filter`, and reserve vectorized code for `map_batches`. "
"Ray Data owns its batch-mode schema inference and conversion rules; see "
"[Ray Data interoperability](ray-data-interop.md)."
msgstr ""
"对于必须在任一后端运行的代码，`map`、`flat_map` 和 `filter` 应优先使用行映射，并将向量化代码留给 "
"`map_batches`。Ray Data 负责批处理模式下的模式推断和转换规则；请参阅 [Ray Data 互操作](ray-data-"
"interop.md)。"

msgid "Choose a transformation"
msgstr "选择转换操作"

msgid "Operation"
msgstr "操作"

msgid "Input and output contract"
msgstr "输入与输出契约"

msgid "Use it for"
msgstr "适用场景"

msgid "`map(fn)`"
msgstr "`map(fn)`"

msgid ""
"One input invocation produces one mapping. With native batching, one "
"column mapping produces one column mapping."
msgstr "一次输入调用生成一个映射。使用原生批处理时，一个列映射生成一个列映射。"

msgid "One-to-one enrichment or replacement."
msgstr "一对一扩充或替换。"

msgid "`map_batches(fn)`"
msgstr "`map_batches(fn)`"

msgid "One columnar batch produces one columnar batch; its row count may change."
msgstr "一个列式批次生成一个列式批次；行数可以变化。"

msgid "Vectorized or accelerator-backed work."
msgstr "向量化或由加速器支持的工作。"

msgid "`flat_map(fn)`"
msgstr "`flat_map(fn)`"

msgid ""
"One input invocation returns or yields zero or more mappings. With native"
" batching, each yielded mapping is a columnar batch."
msgstr "一次输入调用返回或生成零个或多个映射。使用原生批处理时，每个生成的映射都是一个列式批次。"

msgid "Expansion, tokenization, or optional output."
msgstr "展开、分词或可选输出。"

msgid "`filter(fn)`"
msgstr "`filter(fn)`"

msgid ""
"Returns one Boolean per row, or one Boolean sequence per native batch. "
"Retained rows are unchanged."
msgstr "每行返回一个布尔值，或每个原生批次返回一个布尔序列。保留的行不会改变。"

msgid "Row selection."
msgstr "行筛选。"

msgid "`map_reduce(...)`"
msgstr "`map_reduce(...)`"

msgid ""
"Expands each input, processes expanded rows in batches, regroups them, "
"then emits one postprocessed mapping."
msgstr "展开每个输入，分批处理展开后的行，再将其重新分组，最后发出一个后处理映射。"

msgid "A streaming fan-out, batched inference, fan-in pattern."
msgstr "流式扇出、批量推理、扇入模式。"

msgid ""
"All five operations are lazy. They return another `DataStream`; attach a "
"sink and call `execute()` to run them."
msgstr "这五种操作都是惰性的。它们返回另一个 `DataStream`；请附加接收器并调用 `execute()` 来运行。"

msgid "Map one record to one record"
msgstr "将一条记录映射为一条记录"

msgid "`map` is the default choice for row-wise transformations:"
msgstr "`map` 是逐行转换的默认选择："

msgid ""
"The unbatched callable must return exactly one mapping. Returning `None`,"
" a scalar, or a list of rows is invalid in native streaming; use `filter`"
" or `flat_map` for those cardinalities."
msgstr ""
"未批处理的可调用对象必须恰好返回一个映射。在原生流处理中，返回 `None`、标量或行列表均无效；需要这些基数时，请使用 `filter` 或 "
"`flat_map`。"

msgid ""
"`map(batch_size=N)` has a deliberately narrower meaning than "
"`map_batches`. It enables columnar invocations in native streaming, but "
"the Ray Data lowering of `map` remains row-wise. Avoid this form in a "
"graph that may run in batch mode. Prefer `map_batches` when batching is "
"part of the logical UDF contract."
msgstr ""
"`map(batch_size=N)` 的含义有意设计得比 `map_batches` 更窄。它会在原生流处理中启用列式调用，但 `map` 的 "
"Ray Data 下沉仍按行执行。对于可能以批处理模式运行的图，请避免这种形式。当批处理属于逻辑 UDF 契约的一部分时，应优先使用 "
"`map_batches`。"

msgid "Map a vectorized batch"
msgstr "映射向量化批次"

msgid "`map_batches` makes the batch contract explicit:"
msgstr "`map_batches` 明确规定了批处理契约："

msgid ""
"`\"default\"` and `\"numpy\"` expose batches as `dict[str, "
"numpy.ndarray]`. The public API also forwards `\"pandas\"` to Ray Data in"
" batch mode, where the callable receives a `pandas.DataFrame`. Pandas is "
"not a portable native-streaming batch contract; use the NumPy-style "
"mapping when the same graph may select streaming."
msgstr ""
"`\"default\"` 和 `\"numpy\"` 将批次公开为 `dict[str, numpy.ndarray]`。在批处理模式下，公共 "
"API 还会把 `\"pandas\"` 转发给 Ray Data，此时可调用对象接收 `pandas.DataFrame`。Pandas "
"不是可移植的原生流批处理契约；当同一个图可能选择流处理时，请使用 NumPy 风格的映射。"

msgid ""
"In native streaming, `batch_size` is the maximum number of rows in one "
"invocation, not a promise that every batch is full. A partial batch is "
"flushed when its timeout expires, at an end-of-input or "
"checkpoint/control boundary, or when a two-input side changes. In batch "
"mode, Ray Data controls block boundaries and may also supply a smaller "
"batch. The output may contain fewer or more rows than the input, provided"
" all output columns have equal length."
msgstr ""
"在原生流处理中，`batch_size` "
"是单次调用的最大行数，并不保证每个批次都会填满。部分批次会在超时、输入结束、检查点/控制边界或双输入侧发生变化时刷新。在批处理模式下，Ray "
"Data 控制块边界，也可能提供更小的批次。只要所有输出列长度相同，输出行数可以少于或多于输入。"

msgid "Expand with `flat_map`"
msgstr "使用 `flat_map` 展开"

msgid ""
"A `flat_map` callable returns any finite iterable of mappings. A "
"generator is useful when expansion would otherwise allocate a large list:"
msgstr "`flat_map` 可调用对象返回任意有限的映射可迭代对象。当展开操作原本会分配很大的列表时，生成器非常有用："

msgid ""
"Returning an empty iterable drops the input. Values yielded for one "
"invocation are emitted in generator order. A generator is not "
"transactional: if it yields three rows and then raises, those three rows "
"have already been emitted. A retry can emit them again."
msgstr "返回空可迭代对象会丢弃该输入。一次调用生成的值会按生成器顺序发出。生成器不具备事务性：如果它生成三行后抛出异常，这三行已经发出，重试时可能再次发出。"

msgid ""
"When `batch_size` is set in native streaming, the callable receives a "
"column mapping and every yielded value must itself be a valid column "
"mapping. As with `map`, that option does not turn the Ray Data `flat_map`"
" lowering into a batch UDF, so use it only for a deliberately streaming "
"graph."
msgstr ""
"在原生流处理中设置 `batch_size` 后，可调用对象会接收列映射，并且每个生成的值本身都必须是有效的列映射。与 `map` "
"一样，该选项不会将 Ray Data 的 `flat_map` 下沉变成批 UDF，因此仅应在明确使用流处理的图中使用。"

msgid "Filter records"
msgstr "筛选记录"

msgid "An unbatched predicate returns a truth value for one row:"
msgstr "未批处理的谓词为一行返回一个真值："

msgid ""
"With native streaming batching enabled, the predicate receives a column "
"mapping and must return one Boolean decision for every input row:"
msgstr "启用原生流批处理后，谓词接收列映射，并且必须为每个输入行返回一个布尔判定："

msgid ""
"The number of decisions must match the batch length. Retained values are "
"the original input rows; `filter` does not apply changes made to a "
"separate result. Ray Data batch execution continues to use its row-wise "
"`Dataset.filter` contract, so the batched predicate form is native-"
"streaming-only."
msgstr ""
"判定数量必须与批次长度一致。保留的值是原始输入行；`filter` 不会应用对另一结果所做的更改。Ray Data 批处理执行继续使用逐行的 "
"`Dataset.filter` 契约，因此批量谓词形式仅适用于原生流处理。"

msgid "Compose expansion, batching, and regrouping"
msgstr "组合展开、批处理与重新分组"

msgid ""
"`map_reduce` is a native-streaming composite for a common inference "
"pattern:"
msgstr "`map_reduce` 是针对常见推理模式的原生流处理组合操作："

msgid ""
"The preprocess callable expands one input mapping into zero or more "
"mutable row mappings. Klein remembers their original order and identity. "
"The batch callable receives column mappings and must preserve the number "
"of rows while returning equal-length columns. `key_selector` must select "
"the same logical key for every expanded row from one original input. It "
"routes processed rows, and the final callable receives one mapping of "
"lists for that original input in preprocess order."
msgstr ""
"预处理可调用对象将一个输入映射展开为零个或多个可变行映射。Klein "
"会记住它们的原始顺序和身份。批处理可调用对象接收列映射，并且必须在返回等长列的同时保持行数不变。对于同一原始输入展开出的每一行，`key_selector`"
" 必须选择同一个逻辑键。它负责路由处理后的行，最终可调用对象则按预处理顺序接收该原始输入对应的一个列表映射。"

msgid ""
"The three entries in `num_cpus`, `num_gpus`, and `concurrency` configure "
"the preprocess, batch-process, and postprocess stages respectively. Each "
"stage also has its own callable-class constructor arguments. "
"`batch_process_timeout` controls partial streaming batches."
msgstr ""
"`num_cpus`、`num_gpus` 和 `concurrency` "
"中的三个值分别配置预处理、批处理和后处理阶段。每个阶段也有各自的可调用类构造参数。`batch_process_timeout` "
"控制部分流式批次。"

msgid ""
"If preprocessing emits nothing, `MissingDataStrategy.ERROR` fails the "
"invocation, `WARNING` logs and drops it, and `IGNORE` silently drops it. "
"This is separate from the job-wide UDF exception policy. `map_reduce` has"
" no Ray Data lowering; explicitly select streaming for a bounded graph "
"that uses it:"
msgstr ""
"如果预处理未发出任何内容，`MissingDataStrategy.ERROR` 会使调用失败，`WARNING` "
"会记录日志并丢弃输入，`IGNORE` 则静默丢弃。这与作业级 UDF 异常策略相互独立。`map_reduce` 没有 Ray Data "
"下沉；使用它的有界图必须显式选择流处理："

msgid "Callable forms and worker construction"
msgstr "可调用形式与工作节点构造"

msgid ""
"Transforms accept a plain function or a callable class. `flat_map` "
"additionally works naturally with a synchronous generator function."
msgstr "转换接受普通函数或可调用类。`flat_map` 还可以自然地使用同步生成器函数。"

msgid "Form"
msgstr "形式"

msgid "Construction and invocation"
msgstr "构造与调用"

msgid "Plain function or lambda"
msgstr "普通函数或 lambda"

msgid ""
"Serialized with the graph and invoked directly. No runtime context is "
"injected."
msgstr "随图一起序列化并直接调用，不注入运行时上下文。"

msgid "Synchronous generator function"
msgstr "同步生成器函数"

msgid ""
"Supported where the operator expects an iterable, notably `flat_map` and "
"preprocess."
msgstr "当算子期望可迭代对象时受支持，尤其适用于 `flat_map` 和预处理。"

msgid "Callable class type"
msgstr "可调用类类型"

msgid ""
"Instantiated for each worker/subtask, then its `__call__` method is "
"invoked. Pass the class, not an instance."
msgstr "为每个工作节点/子任务实例化，然后调用其 `__call__` 方法。请传入类，而不是实例。"

msgid "`async def` callable"
msgstr "`async def` 可调用对象"

msgid "Native streaming support requires a positive `async_buffer_size`."
msgstr "原生流处理支持要求 `async_buffer_size` 为正数。"

msgid "Async generator"
msgstr "异步生成器"

msgid ""
"Not supported; use an async coroutine that returns an ordinary finite "
"iterable for `flat_map`."
msgstr "不受支持；对于 `flat_map`，请使用返回普通有限可迭代对象的异步协程。"

msgid "Constructor arguments are valid only with a callable class:"
msgstr "构造参数仅适用于可调用类："

msgid ""
"If a callable class constructor has a parameter literally named "
"`runtime_context`, Klein supplies it as a keyword argument. Do not also "
"provide that keyword. The read-only context exposes:"
msgstr ""
"如果可调用类的构造函数有一个名称恰好为 `runtime_context` 的参数，Klein "
"会以关键字参数形式提供它。请勿同时自行提供该关键字。只读上下文公开："

msgid "`task_name`, `task_index`, and `parallelism`;"
msgstr "`task_name`、`task_index` 和 `parallelism`；"

msgid "the effective job `config`;"
msgstr "生效的作业 `config`；"

msgid "the operator `metric_group`;"
msgstr "算子的 `metric_group`；"

msgid "`runtime_info`, including batching and async settings;"
msgstr "`runtime_info`，包括批处理和异步设置；"

msgid "`job_id`, which is the live job namespace in native streaming."
msgstr "`job_id`，在原生流处理中即实时作业命名空间。"

msgid ""
"In Ray Data batch execution, the context is a compiler-side operator "
"context; Ray Data owns physical worker identities, so `task_index` and "
"`parallelism` are not streaming subtask coordinates. Do not use them for "
"batch partitioning."
msgstr ""
"在 Ray Data 批处理执行中，该上下文是编译器侧的算子上下文；Ray Data 负责物理工作节点身份，因此 `task_index` 和 "
"`parallelism` 并不是流处理子任务坐标。请勿用它们进行批分区。"

msgid ""
"An ordinary callable class has construction but no managed "
"`open()`/`close()` lifecycle. Build per-worker immutable helpers in its "
"constructor. For resources that require deterministic cleanup or "
"checkpoint participation, implement a documented source/sink lifecycle "
"instead of relying on a transform object's destructor."
msgstr ""
"普通可调用类具有构造过程，但没有受管的 `open()`/`close()` "
"生命周期。请在其构造函数中创建每个工作节点专属的不可变辅助对象。对于需要确定性清理或参与检查点的资源，请实现文档所述的源/接收器生命周期，而不要依赖转换对象的析构函数。"

msgid "Batching, timeouts, and ordered async I/O"
msgstr "批处理、超时与有序异步 I/O"

msgid "The common tuning arguments describe different limits:"
msgstr "常见调优参数描述不同的限制："

msgid ""
"`batch_size` bounds rows per native-streaming invocation. `None` disables"
" batching; positive integers enable it."
msgstr "`batch_size` 限制每次原生流处理调用的行数。`None` 禁用批处理；正整数启用批处理。"

msgid ""
"`batch_timeout` bounds how long a partial native-streaming batch waits "
"after its first row. It is meaningful only when batching is enabled."
msgstr "`batch_timeout` 限制原生流处理的部分批次在收到第一行后等待的时长。它仅在启用批处理时有意义。"

msgid ""
"`async_buffer_size` bounds concurrent async invocations in each streaming"
" subtask. It must be a positive integer when set."
msgstr "`async_buffer_size` 限制每个流处理子任务中的并发异步调用数。设置时必须为正整数。"

msgid ""
"`concurrency` controls physical operator parallelism; `num_cpus` and "
"`num_gpus` are the resources requested for each operator worker."
msgstr "`concurrency` 控制物理算子并行度；`num_cpus` 和 `num_gpus` 是每个算子工作节点请求的资源。"

msgid ""
"For `map_batches`, Ray Data receives `batch_size` and `batch_format` in "
"batch mode, but not the streaming timeout. For `map`, `flat_map`, and "
"`filter`, Ray Data uses its row-wise operation and does not receive "
"Klein's streaming batch settings. `async_buffer_size` is a native-"
"streaming execution window, not a Ray Data concurrency option."
msgstr ""
"对于 `map_batches`，Ray Data 在批处理模式下会接收 `batch_size` 和 "
"`batch_format`，但不会接收流处理超时。对于 `map`、`flat_map` 和 `filter`，Ray Data "
"使用逐行操作，不接收 Klein 的流批处理设置。`async_buffer_size` 是原生流处理执行窗口，而不是 Ray Data "
"并发选项。"

msgid "An async transform must opt in explicitly:"
msgstr "异步转换必须显式启用："

msgid ""
"Klein starts at most `async_buffer_size` calls per subtask. Calls may "
"complete out of order, but results are emitted in input order. A "
"checkpoint barrier or other control message is queued behind all earlier "
"invocations, so it cannot overtake their output. When the window is full,"
" upstream consumption waits; this is backpressure, not record dropping."
msgstr ""
"Klein 每个子任务最多启动 `async_buffer_size` "
"个调用。调用可以乱序完成，但结果会按输入顺序发出。检查点屏障或其他控制消息会排在所有更早的调用之后，因此无法越过它们的输出。窗口已满时，上游消费会等待；这是反压，并非丢弃记录。"

msgid ""
"Set `async_buffer_size` only for an awaitable callable. Without it, an "
"async function is invoked through the synchronous path and its coroutine "
"is not a valid record. With it, a synchronous return value cannot be "
"awaited. For async `flat_map`, the coroutine must resolve to an ordinary "
"iterable of mappings."
msgstr ""
"仅对可等待的可调用对象设置 "
"`async_buffer_size`。未设置时，异步函数会通过同步路径调用，其协程不是有效记录；设置后，同步返回值又无法被等待。对于异步 "
"`flat_map`，协程必须解析为普通的映射可迭代对象。"

msgid ""
"Synchronous invocations are serialized within each native streaming "
"subtask. Parallelism comes from multiple subtasks. Ordering is therefore "
"defined per input channel/subtask; shuffles and parallel union branches "
"do not establish a global order."
msgstr ""
"同步调用在每个原生流处理子任务内串行执行。并行性来自多个子任务。因此，顺序仅在每个输入通道/子任务内定义；洗牌和并行 union "
"分支不会建立全局顺序。"

msgid "Exceptions, retries, and data loss"
msgstr "异常、重试与数据丢失"

msgid ""
"The default `udf.ignore-exception=false` propagates a UDF exception. The "
"task fails, and streaming recovery may replay data from a checkpoint. "
"Batch-mode failure and retry behavior belongs to Ray Data."
msgstr ""
"默认的 `udf.ignore-exception=false` 会传播 UDF "
"异常。任务会失败，流恢复可能从检查点重放数据。批处理模式的失败和重试行为由 Ray Data 定义。"

msgid ""
"Setting the option to `true` logs the error, increments the UDF exception"
" metric, and continues with later input:"
msgstr "将该选项设为 `true` 会记录错误、递增 UDF 异常指标，并继续处理后续输入："

msgid ""
"In `auto` mode this setting selects native streaming even for an "
"otherwise batch-lowerable bounded graph. Ray Data's block-level error "
"policy does not provide the same per-record continuation and Klein metric"
" semantics."
msgstr ""
"在 `auto` 模式下，即使有界图原本可以完全下沉为批处理，启用此设置也会选择"
"原生流处理。Ray Data 的块级错误策略无法提供相同的逐记录继续处理语义和 "
"Klein 指标语义。"

msgid ""
"This is an explicit data-loss policy, not a dead-letter queue. A failed "
"sync or async invocation normally emits no result, which can corrupt "
"aggregates, joins, state, and source-to-sink accounting. A synchronous "
"`flat_map` generator is an additional edge case: rows yielded before the "
"exception remain emitted, so ignoring the exception does not make that "
"input atomically dropped. Keep the default unless the missing-output "
"behavior is acceptable and observable."
msgstr ""
"这是一项显式的数据丢失策略，不是死信队列。失败的同步或异步调用通常不发出任何结果，这可能破坏聚合、连接、状态以及源到接收器的计数。同步 "
"`flat_map` "
"生成器还有一个边界情况：异常前生成的行仍已发出，因此忽略异常不会以原子方式丢弃该输入。除非缺少输出的行为可以接受且可观测，否则请保留默认值。"

msgid "Serialization and external side effects"
msgstr "序列化与外部副作用"

msgid ""
"Klein and Ray serialize UDFs, closures, callable classes, and constructor"
" arguments to execute them away from the driver. Do not capture open "
"sockets, file handles, locks, event loops, or other non-serializable "
"driver state. Ship small immutable configuration and construct clients on"
" the worker instead. Mutable driver globals are not shared state between "
"workers."
msgstr ""
"Klein 和 Ray 会序列化 "
"UDF、闭包、可调用类及构造参数，以便在驱动程序之外执行。请勿捕获已打开的套接字、文件句柄、锁、事件循环或其他不可序列化的驱动程序状态。应传递小型不可变配置，并改为在工作节点上构造客户端。可变的驱动程序全局变量并不是工作节点之间的共享状态。"

msgid ""
"Worker failure can re-run an invocation. Generator output can be "
"replayed, and an external request can succeed even if its acknowledgement"
" is lost before a checkpoint. Make transform-side effects idempotent "
"using a stable event key, or move effects to a sink with the required "
"delivery protocol. See [delivery and consistency guarantees](delivery-"
"semantics.md)."
msgstr ""
"工作节点故障可能重新执行一次调用。生成器输出可能被重放，即使外部请求已经成功，其确认也可能在检查点前丢失。请使用稳定的事件键使转换副作用具备幂等性，或将副作用移至具有所需交付协议的接收器。请参阅[交付与一致性保证"
"](delivery-semantics.md)。"

msgid ""
"Do not keep correctness-critical aggregation state in a callable-class "
"field. It is local to one worker and is not automatically checkpointed or"
" repartitioned. Use [managed keyed state](ray-native-state.md) for "
"recoverable state."
msgstr ""
"不要把影响正确性的关键聚合状态保存在可调用类字段中。它只存在于一个工作节点本地，不会自动进入检查点或重新分区。可恢复状态应使用[托管键控状态"
"](ray-native-state.md)。"

msgid "Partition, merge, and chain streams"
msgstr "对流进行分区、合并与链化"

msgid ""
"The partitioning calls `broadcast()`, `rescale()`, `round_robin()`, "
"`adaptive_shuffle()`, and `partition_by(...)` configure the outgoing edge"
" used by the **next** native-streaming operator. Apply them immediately "
"before that consumer:"
msgstr ""
"分区调用 `broadcast()`、`rescale()`、`round_robin()`、`adaptive_shuffle()` 和 "
"`partition_by(...)` 会配置供**下一个**原生流处理算子使用的出边。请紧挨着相应消费者之前调用它们："

msgid ""
"`key_by(selector)` is different: it creates stable key-group routing for "
"stateful processing, windows, joins, and rescaling. Read [managed state"
"](ray-native-state.md) before choosing keys or max parallelism. These "
"edge methods do not repartition a Ray Data batch; use the matching "
"`stream.data` operation for batch partitioning."
msgstr ""
"`key_by(selector)` 与之不同：它会为有状态处理、窗口、连接和伸缩创建稳定的键组路由。选择键或最大并行度之前，请阅读[托管状态"
"](ray-native-state.md)。这些边方法不会重新分区 Ray Data 批次；批分区应使用对应的 `stream.data` "
"操作。"

msgid ""
"`left.union(right, ...)` requires every input to belong to the same "
"internal pipeline. It merges the branches but defines no total order "
"between them. Each branch retains its own upstream order until scheduling"
" or a downstream shuffle interleaves records. In batch mode, union "
"delegates to Ray Data."
msgstr ""
"`left.union(right, ...)` "
"要求每个输入都属于同一个内部管道。它会合并分支，但不定义分支之间的全序。每个分支保持各自的上游顺序，直至调度或下游洗牌将记录交错。在批处理模式下，union"
" 委托给 Ray Data。"

msgid ""
"Native streaming enables operator chaining by default. Compatible "
"stateless, synchronous operators connected by a forward edge can share "
"one task and avoid an actor hop. Chaining requires matching CPU/GPU, "
"concurrency, batch-size, and async-buffer contracts. A shuffle, multiple "
"upstreams, managed state, async execution, or different resources creates"
" a boundary. Chaining changes physical placement, not record semantics. "
"Disable `pipeline.operator-chaining.enabled` when diagnosing lifecycle "
"behavior or when an operator must remain an independent scaling unit."
msgstr ""
"原生流处理默认启用算子链化。通过前向边连接且兼容的无状态同步算子可以共享一个任务，从而避免一次 actor 跳转。链化要求 "
"CPU/GPU、并发度、批大小和异步缓冲区契约一致。洗牌、多个上游、托管状态、异步执行或不同资源都会形成边界。链化改变的是物理放置，而不是记录语义。在诊断生命周期行为或需要让算子保持独立伸缩单元时，请禁用"
" `pipeline.operator-chaining.enabled`。"

